sythesis 

first add all the verilog codes in one file
now launch genus inside cadence by -  genus
		now run these commands one by one or make tcl file (for runnuing tcl file and type genus -f your_file_name.tcl)

				# -------- Library Setup --------
set_db lib_search_path {/home/install/FOUNDRY/digital/45nm/dig/lib}
set_db library {slow.lib}

# -------- Read RTL --------
read_hdl delay_line.v
read_hdl precomputer.v
read_hdl tap_mult.v
read_hdl fir_filter.v

# Set top module
elaborate fir_filter

# -------- Constraints --------
read_sdc fir.sdc

# -------- Synthesis Effort --------
set_db syn_generic_effort medium
set_db syn_map_effort medium
set_db syn_opt_effort medium

# -------- Synthesis Flow --------
syn_generic
syn_map
syn_opt

gui_show

# -------- Reports --------
report_timing > timing.rpt
report_area > area.rpt
report_power > power.rpt
report_gates > gate.rpt
# -------- Netlist --------
write_hdl > fir_synth.v
write_sdc > fir_tool.sdc






